title: Vysokovo, Kovrovsky District, Vladimir Oblast
text:
Vysokovo () is a <a href="types%20of%20inhabited%20localities%20in%20Russia">rural locality</a> (a <a href="Village%23Russia">village</a>) in Malyginskoye Rural Settlement, <a href="Kovrovsky%20District">Kovrovsky District</a>, <a href="Vladimir%20Oblast">Vladimir Oblast</a>, Russia. The population was 10 as of 2010.
Geography.
Vysokovo is located 23 km north of <a href="Kovrov">Kovrov</a> (the district's administrative centre) by road. Koromyslovo is the nearest rural locality.
